title: Top 10 plays: Cousins gets dunked on, Richard Jefferson time travels
text:
56p ET 
After a hefty slate of preseason games Wednesday, it truly feels like the NBA is back. Thirteen NBA teams were in action (plus a Brazilian team, Bayru, which faced the Knicks ), and they produced the first full batch of higlights in the 2015-16 season. 
Check out the top 10 plays from Wednesday's preseason slate, featuring a halfcourt shot from the Knicks' Cleanthony Early , Sacramento Kings big man DeMarcus Cousins ending up on a poster, an unconventional block from rookie Kristaps Porzingis and a dunk from Cleveland Cavaliers veteran Richard Jefferson that will have you wondering what year it is: true
